{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/edit-keyboard-layout","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>I keep accidentally typing <code class=\"language-text\">Shift-Space</code> which inserts a non-breaking space instead of a regular space. That's why I wanted to edit my keyboard layout. The following example shows how to change <code class=\"language-text\">Shift-Space</code> to insert a regular space.</p>\n<h2 id=\"edit-layout\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#edit-layout\" aria-label=\"edit layout permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Edit layout</h2>\n<p>On my machine (Fedora) the file is located here:</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`/usr/share/X11/xkb/symbols/ch`, ``)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">/usr/share/X11/xkb/symbols/ch</code></pre></div>\n<p>Search for the correct line and change it like this:</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`- key <SPCE> { [\tspace, \tnobreakspace,\tnobreakspace\t\t]\t};\n+ key <SPCE> { [\tspace, \tspace,\t      nobreakspace\t\t]\t};`, ``)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"diff\"><pre class=\"language-diff\"><code class=\"language-diff\"><span class=\"token deleted-sign deleted\"><span class=\"token prefix deleted\">-</span> key &lt;SPCE> { [\tspace, \tnobreakspace,\tnobreakspace\t\t]\t};\n</span><span class=\"token inserted-sign inserted\"><span class=\"token prefix inserted\">+</span> key &lt;SPCE> { [\tspace, \tspace,\t      nobreakspace\t\t]\t};</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"apply-changes\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#apply-changes\" aria-label=\"apply changes permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Apply changes</h2>\n<p>In order to apply the changes the layout needs to be set again. In my case:</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`setxkbmap ch de_mac`, ``)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">setxkbmap ch de_mac</code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"path":"/edit-keyboard-layout","title":"Edit keyboard layout on Linux","date":"2022-10-23","tags":["linux","keyboard layout"],"source":"https://vi.stackexchange.com/a/12014"}}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864","63159454"]}